<para id="fs-idm228289760">The ICE table defines x as the hydronium ion molarity, and so the pH is computed as</para>
<equation id="fs-idm247349056"><m:math>
 <m:mrow>
  <m:mtext>pH</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mtext>log</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">[</m:mo><m:msub>
   <m:mtext>H</m:mtext>
   <m:mn>3</m:mn>
  </m:msub>
  <m:msup>
   <m:mtext>O</m:mtext>
